1. .insert()、.append() 方法均不存在：tuple本身不支持增加元素，报错信息为 AttributeError: &#39;tuple&#39; object has no attribute &#39;remove&#39;
2. .remove() 同理；del 删除元素 报不支持该命令：TypeError: &#39;tuple&#39; object doesn&#39;t support item deletion
3. 不存在第四个元素，因此报索引错误：IndexError: tuple index out of range

demo2=(&#39;x&#39;,&#39;y&#39;,&#39;z&#39;)
# print(demo2.insert(0,1)) #&#39;tuple&#39; object has no attribute &#39;insert&#39;
# print(demo2.remove(0)) #&#39;tuple&#39; object has no attribute &#39;remove&#39;
# print(demo2[3]) #tuple index out of range
